trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperty>" name="<EncryptionProperty>" href=""></xref> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperty>" name="<EncryptionProperty>" href=""> </xref> element som brukes i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The EncryptionProperty class encapsulates the `<EncryptionProperty>` element defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EncryptionProperty innkapsler den `<EncryptionProperty>` elementet definert i World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering spesifikasjonen finnes på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: Use the EncryptionProperty class to provide additional encryption information related to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: Bruke klassen EncryptionProperty til å gi flere krypteringsinformasjonen som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>og <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>elementer.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: For example, use this class to specify a time stamp.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel bruke denne klassen til å angi et tidsstempel.
